OL,9,Flifelong consequences of forced
OL,10,Fadoptions in the UK
OL,12,FAn ITV investigation has found
OL,13,Fchilling evidence that unmarried
OL,14,Fmothers in England fear they were
OL,15,Fgiven a dangerous drug now linked to
OL,16,Fcancers and other serious conditions
OL,17,Fwhile in state institutions in the
OL,18,F1950s, 60s and 70s.
