OL,6,FYet in UK, the true extent of the harm
OL,7,Fcaused and the numbers exposed to
OL,8,Fdiethylstilbestrol is still unknown
OL,9,Fpartly due to a lack of medical
OL,10,Frecords. It's been described by some
OL,11,Fdoctors as 'the silent thalidomide.'
OL,13,FConsultant Urogynaecologist and
OL,14,Fadvisor to the Scottish Government Dr
OL,15,FWael Agurhas treated women who were
OL,16,Fexposed to the drug.
OL,18,F"The most serious risk is the cancer
OL,19,Frisk," he told ITV Tonight.
