OL,6,FAs a 16-year-old, pregnant and
OL,7,Funmarried, she was sent to a home in
OL,8,FSouthampton in 1974.She recalls her
OL,9,Fbreast milk drying up after having an
OL,10,Finjection in the hospital.
OL,12,F"I have tried to find out what that
OL,13,Fdrug was. I've approached the
OL,14,Fhospital, I've tried NHS records, but
OL,15,Fso far I've drawn a blank," Ms
OL,16,FDefries, who is now 67, said.
OL,18,FDiana Defries says she has no idea
OL,19,Fwhat drug she was given as a teenager
OL,20,Fat a mother and baby home in
OL,21,FSouthampton in 1974
