OL,6,FITV Tonight has spoken to former
OL,7,Fnurses who remember DES being
OL,8,Fadministered throughout the 1970s, and
OL,9,Fseveral women who suspect they were
OL,10,Fgiven the medication in mother and
OL,11,Fbaby homes, and hospitals, across the
OL,12,Fcountry.
